data.description: Welcome Home.  2.5% assumable loan!  This is a wonderful opportunity to have your getaway at the Coves.  This home sits on the golf course and is a quick golf cart ride to Cherokee Yacht Club and Marina.  You have super easy access to the lake and you have tons of amenities, too many to list.  The home has newer flooring and the roof was replaced in 2020.  Don't miss out on this great opportunity to live at the lake or have a wonderful weekend retreat. BIG price reduction, spend Christmas on the lake!!!
